imagingbook
This package contains the common library used by the ImageJ plugins provided for Digital Image Processing books authored by Wilhelm Burger and Mark J Burge, published by Springer.
imagingbook.lib
This package contains general utility classes used in demo plugins and in library classes in the 'pub' package.
